casebody.data:
Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Woollams.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. Woollams (1988), 40 Ohio St. 3d 603.]

(No. D.D. 88-22 Submitted November 2, 1988 Decided December 7, 1988.)

Richard C. Woollams, Jr. is publicly reprimanded.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
